---
import { Code } from 'astro:components';
import Starter from '../layouts/Starter.astro';
---
<Starter>
	<center>
		<h1>Setup Done!</h1>
	</center>

	<p>You can now stop your dev server and add the following option in your astro.config to start using Astro-StudioCMS then start back up to see your new CMS data</p>

	<Code lang="diff" code={`import { defineConfig } from "astro/config";
import astroStudioCMS from "@astrolicious/studiocms";
import db from '@astrojs/db';

// https://astro.build/config
export default defineConfig({
    // other config options,
	integrations: [
		db(),
		astroStudioCMS({ 
+			dbStartPage: false,
		}),
	],
});`}/>

</Starter>